766d642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n一日支那籍，一世支那奴隸<br />\n我地要攞番做人啲尊嚴"},{"pid":"6ef3d9a571268e74853b5addaec9c5a90802622f","tid":1507194,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de3553c52562d26c3953c7f2c4fe5dac3840bec","tid":1507194,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db67c2ac77cf76560529891f824cd26206411b1","tid":1507194,"uid":88664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60e85b79935e8b7322ddb7df48e9564cd56ee5fd","tid":1507194,"uid":208573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:10:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=8766d642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫下手，而家仲爭大約四萬個網上簽名 ，儲齊10萬個簽名，就可以畀壓力英國議會，將呢個話題擺上會議討論 。<br />\n<br />\n目的係想將擁有bno passport嘅15至16萬個市民可以拎到英國居英權 。其實唔只呢15至16萬個市民嘅，因為如果佢哋拎到居英權，佢哋嘅直屬家屬，甚至乎伴侶，都可以拎到英國居英權。<br />\n<br />\n 而且喺香港仲有好多人其實係冇續令到bno passport。只要你一日有keep住嗰本舊嘅英國bno passport，你都仲可以續領一本新嘅passport。所以數字上係絕對唔止十六萬咁少。<br />\n<br />\n其實佢個deadline好快就到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家幫下手，畫隻龜簽名，就可以畀壓力比英國，俾壓力比香港政府同埋中國 。<br />\n<br />\n如果你撳入去，你會留意到佢淨係畀有英國護照嘅人或者目前住喺英國嘅居民先可以簽名，但其實你只要求其喺google搵一個英國postcode填上去就ok㗎喇。你淨係需要填上你嘅姓名電郵同埋postcode。你個姓名都唔一定需要係你嘅真名 ，希望大家如果可以除咗畫隻龜之餘，都將啲條link share畀身邊嘅朋友。成個過程唔會嘥你多過三分鐘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:33:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"61564d1de8751fc564c2efbcaf5ceb8c3352f11d","tid":1507194,"uid":278283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:42:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=8766d642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n盡推, 越多越好"},{"pid":"b2a6522972aace7c89922a90e1093d2830ea0024","tid":1507194,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kkYJbJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkkYJbJM.jpg&h=c662ceff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bX1e2Qr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbX1e2Qr.jpg&h=22d1ca8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2076d0dd3f17a51d77d1d55a5cc16d919186dab3","tid":1507194,"uid":267461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"差3萬個ja, 推！"},{"pid":"c6ed9975fbbab1c2b8d8c9324bbf2d4946307969","tid":1507194,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed3b2b6a78ebdf1dbaed76cc72d60ce1fd975178","tid":1507194,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:19:26.000Z","ms